Usage: ./sniffer [OPTION] [VALUE]
For a selected number of packet to be captured the following files are created
	2 Files are created after the end of capturing
		1) pfp_log: Contains all the network flows and payload size sequneces
					found in the given pcap file
		2) pkt_log: Per Packet information
		3) dumpfile: Contains the packets the got captured in a pcap format able
					 to be opened by Wireshark for further analysis 

Available Options:
		-f		Apply a bpf filter 
		-n 		Number of total packets to capture, if no number is
				specified the capture stops by pressing Control^C
